# Vercel Deployments (Reference)
VERCEL_DEPLOYMENT_URL=https://your-project.vercel.app
VERCEL_PROJECT=your-vercel-project-name

# Additional Sharded/Per-Cron Overrides (Example)
# CRON_SCHEDULE_001=0 */15 * * *
# ... up to CRON_SCHEDULE_120

# ========================================
# Deployment Notes
# - Vercel: Use preview/staging only; production secrets should come from Vault-backed platform secrets
# - Azure: Prefer workload identity or App Service/Container App secret references sourced from Vault
# - Akash: Use deploy/akash/entrypoint.sh and deploy/akash/deployment.sdl.tmpl.yml
# - Security: Never commit real values; never print secrets; rotate AppRole SecretIDs for each deployment